{
  "title": "Gentle Bitter Syrian Lamb Stew",
  "description": "A traditional Syrian stew with bitter notes, made with lamb and celery salt, poached to perfection in a mason jar, suitable for a satvik diet. This one-pot dish is a hearty and comforting meal.",
